      "body" : "Yes, need the line number, it can't be 864 anymore. Also need output of:\r\n```\r\nautoconf --version\r\nautomake --version\r\nm4 --version\r\n```\r\n\r\nI guess it's triggered by this, but don't ask me what it does (looks like a no-op):\r\n```\r\nPKGCONFIG_LIBDIR_TEMP=\"$PKG_CONFIG_LIBDIR\"\r\nunset PKG_CONFIG_LIBDIR\r\nPKG_CONFIG_LIBDIR=\"$PKGCONFIG_LIBDIR_TEMP\"\r\n````\r\n@theuni can you take a look? Don't know what CentOS does differently.\r\n",
